00:08:58.260 --> 00:09:00.510 align:middle line:84%
And I see flashes of
color quite a bit.

00:09:00.510 --> 00:09:03.600 align:middle line:84%
I see this rug,
for example, seems

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:05.820 align:middle line:84%
