lot of complements

00:09:05.820 --> 00:09:08.550 align:middle line:90%
of violet and yellow.

00:09:08.550 --> 00:09:12.240 align:middle line:84%
It seems to feel that
I'm going to watch it.

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:16.080 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, as it turned out, the
experience is not at all like

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:18.750 align:middle line:84%
