of a schizophrenic is.

00:09:18.750 --> 00:09:21.960 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, when you look at
your hands, do as I do.

00:09:21.960 --> 00:09:25.300 align:middle line:84%
Close your eyes, and just
concentrate on your hands.

00:09:25.300 --> 00:09:26.100 align:middle line:90%
>> There it is.

00:09:26.100 --> 00:09:29.070 align:middle line:84%
I feel these lovely colors
vibrating all over me.

00:09:29.070 --> 00:09:30.060 align:middle line:90%
Oh, it's lovely.

00:09:30.060 --> 00:09:31.000 align:middle line:90%
>> Any lines?

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:31.800 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh.

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:33.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Any forms?

00:09:33.390 --> 00:09:36.480 align:middle line:84%
>> Just like the
shimmering water, you know?

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.530 align:middle line:84%
>> You can put
your hand down now.

00:09:38.530 --> 00:09:39.330 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:09:39.330 --> 00:09:42.210 align:middle line:90%
Describe it.

00:09:42.210 --> 00:09:43.598 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, I don't know.

00:09:43.598 --> 00:09:44.534 align:middle line:90%
>> Hmm?

00:09:44.534 --> 00:09:48.750 align:middle line:90%


00:09:48.750 --> 00:09:50.270 align:middle line:90%
>> It's just giving, and--

00:09:50.270 --> 00:09:59.650 align:middle line:90%


00:09:59.650 --> 00:10:01.876 align:middle line:90%
you don't know.

00:10:01.876 --> 00:10:05.660 align:middle line:90%
You want to give yourself--

00:10:05.660 --> 00:10:08.008 align:middle line:84%
you want to give yourself
as much as you can.

00:10:08.008 --> 00:10:10.550 align:middle line:84%
>> There's all sorts of things
happening during a psychedelic

00:10:10.550 --> 00:10:11.350 align:middle line:90%
experience.

00:10:11.350 --> 00:10:14.510 align:middle line:10%
One thing is that the
5-HT2A receptor, which

00:10:14.510 --> 00:10:17.910 align:middle line:10%
