being stimulated quite a bit.

00:10:17.910 --> 00:10:19.170 align:middle line:90%
And that's mostly serotonin.

00:10:19.170 --> 00:10:21.290 align:middle line:84%
But then it turns out
that if you stimulate

00:10:21.290 --> 00:10:24.710 align:middle line:84%
