with a whole other transmitter

00:10:28.730 --> 00:10:30.380 align:middle line:90%
system, which is oxytocin.

00:10:30.380 --> 00:10:32.240 align:middle line:90%
They form what's called a dimer.

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:35.050 align:middle line:84%
They dimerize, and they
create a receptor complex.

00:10:35.050 --> 00:10:37.050 align:middle line:84%
In a couple, when you
fall in love with someone,

00:10:37.050 --> 00:10:39.260 align:middle line:84%
there's a lot of oxytocin,
